Description:
    Creates the standard Viget Labs deployment configuration. The basename of RAILS_ROOT
    is used as the name of the application. This can be overridden by passing an application
    name as the first argument.

Examples:
    `./script/generate viget_deployment`

        creates staging environment in config/environments by copying production
        creates database.yml for mysql, with staging environment
        creates Capfile, config/deploy.rb, config/deploy/production.rb
            and config/deploy/staging.rb
